= Libraries =

# Tornado and Mongo prerequisites
sudo easy_install setuptools pycurl==7.16.2.1 simplejson pymongo
# Tornado
wget http://www.tornadoweb.org/static/tornado-0.2.tar.gz
tar xvf tornado-0.2.tar.gz
cd tornado 0.2
sudo python setup.py install

You also need the latest MongoDB running (v1.4.2) for geospatial indexing.

= Running the server =

In the project root directory, resale_web, do

python resale_web.py

= Conventions =

JSON methods return {'result':'OK'} or {'result':'failure', 'message':...}
